http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#com.@value:
The merged ontology containing the Automation I4.0 Core ontology, the Discrete Dynamics Model Ontology, and the Minified Standards Ontology.
It represents a meta model for automation systems related to the Industry 4.0, Smart Manufacturing, and Industrial Internet of Things (IIoT).
